  <brief_title>Study of the Influence of the Expression of the Calcium-sensitive Receptor (CaSR) by Monocytes in the Synovial Liquid on Structural Alterations in Patients Diagnosed With Rheumatoid Arthritis in the Previous Two Years</brief_title>
  <acronym>CASPER</acronym>
